snippet.textDisplay: This is the traditional custom of teaching elephants to the Maran tribe, one of the ethnic groups of Assam.  Today we are proud that this traditional elephant has been taught in my village and today the whole world has seen it.  Thank you to those who have expressed it so beautifully in music and video.  You can also come to our village once , enjoy the tradition of teaching elephants.
